## Development

```bash
uv sync              # Install dependencies
uv run lazyclaude    # Run app
```

Publish:

```bash
export UV_PUBLISH_TOKEN=<your_token>
uv build
uv publish
```

See: <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/guides/package/>
